# Web games

- Stable game loop; avoid unbounded work per frame; profile on low-end devices.
- Multiplayer: clear authority model; document cheat tolerance for browser clients.
- Asset loading: batch, release resources on scene change; watch memory on long sessions.
- Web3: keep signing UX explicit; coordinate on-chain rules with `defi-protocol-engineer`.
- Use `game-web-engineer` persona; backend lobbies with `fullstack-developer`.
